中国媒体广泛报道事件<ref name=ft00144>{{cite news |url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/8083cb12-6af1-11de-861d-00144feabdc0.html |title=Beijing handles political management of riots |first=Richard |last=McGregor |work=Financial Times |date=2009-07-07 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090708081620/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/8083cb12-6af1-11de-861d-00144feabdc0.html |archivedate=2009-07-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。军队平息事态后不久，政府邀请境外记者到乌鲁木齐实地考察<ref name=nyt090708/>。100多家媒体的记者住进市区[[乌鲁木齐海德酒店|海德酒店]]<ref name=SCMPoverseas/><ref name=DemocracyNowvideo>{{cite news | date=2009-07-09 | accessdate=2009-09-05 | title=Report from Urumqi: Thousands of Chinese Troops Enter City Torn by Ethnic Clashes | format=video | publisher=Democracy Now! | url=http://www.democracynow.org/2009/7/9/report_from_urumqi_thousands_of_chinese | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090904021714/http://www.democracynow.org/2009/7/9/report_from_urumqi_thousands_of_chinese | archivedate=2009-09-04 | dead-url=no }}（对媒体报道的讨论起于26:49，对网络封锁的讨论起于29:00）</ref>，共用30个网络链接<ref name=SCMPoverseas/>。记者们还意外探访了事发地点和医院<ref name=pfteleg090707>{{cite news |url=http://blogs.telegraph.co.uk/news/peterfoster/100002368/uighur-unrest-not-another-tiananmen/ |title=Uighur unrest: not another Tiananmen |work=The Daily Telegraph |first=Peter |last=Foster |date=2009-07-07 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |location=London |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20120707024531/http://blogs.telegraph.co.uk/news/peterfoster/100002368/uighur-unrest-not-another-tiananmen/ |archivedate=2012-07-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《金融时报》称官方这次的处理手段获得很大的改善，跟[[2008年西藏骚乱|2008年西藏骚乱]]的“公关灾难”形成鲜明对比<ref name=ft00144/>。

为在事件过后立即缓和紧张局势，官方立刻在新疆各地开始歌颂民族和谐的大规模宣传活动。当地的节目将维吾尔族歌手和汉族歌手叫在一起，高唱“我们是一家人”。骚乱期间维吾尔族的“英勇事迹”受到传颂，包着标语的宣传车在街道上巡逻，其中一条警告人们要坚决反对恐怖主义、分裂主义和极端主义“[[三股势力|三股势力]]”<ref name=SCMPpropaganda>{{cite news |title=Propaganda shows of Han-Uygur unity fall flat in Silk Road oasis town |work=South China Morning Post |date=2009-07-17 |agency=Associated Press |page= A7}}</ref>。

中共中央总书记[[胡锦涛|胡锦涛]]提前离开[[第35届八国集团首脑会议|意大利八国集团峰会]]<ref name=HuG8/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-07/09/content_11681173.htm |title=Hu holds key meeting on Xinjiang riot, vowing severe punishment on culprits |agency=Xinhua |publisher=Chinaview.cn |last=Guo |first=Likun |author2=Li, Huizi |date=2009-07-07 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090831093008/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-07/09/content_11681173.htm |archivedate=2009-08-31 }}</ref>，召开[[中共中央政治局|中共中央政治局]]紧急会议，派遣中共中央政治局常委、中央政法委书记[[周永康|周永康]]前往新疆“指导维稳工作”<ref>{{cite news |title=Hu Jin-tao sends Zhou Yong-kang to Xinjiang to direct safety work |work=China News Wrap |date=2009-07-10}}</ref>。《南华早报》引述政府消息，指北京将重新评估10月份[[首都各界庆祝中华人民共和国成立60周年大会|建国六十周年庆祝活动]]的各项安排<ref name=SCMPcaughtout>{{cite news |title=Hu's return seen as sign Beijing was caught out |work=South China Morning Post |date=2009-07-09 |first=Kristine |last=Kwok |page= A4}}</ref>。[[中国共产党广东省委员会|中共广东省委]]书记[[汪洋_(1955年)|汪洋]]认为政府的民族政策“绝对需要调整”，否则“会有麻烦”<ref>{{cite news |last=Pomfret |first=James |date=2009-07-30 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2009/07/30/us-china-xinjiang-idUSTRE56T1XJ20090730 |title=China needs new policies after Xinjiang: official |agency=Reuters |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131212113409/http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/07/30/us-china-xinjiang-idUSTRE56T1XJ20090730 |archivedate=2013-12-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。负责安保协调的人员表示，当局计划在建国六十周年活动前从地方派出所调遣警察，预计负责任务的警察有13万人<ref name=FT5aa932ee/>。

事发后，中華人民共和国政府向热比娅计划访问的国家施加外交压力，印度“在北京的建议下”取消了热比娅的签证<ref>{{cite news | last=Jacob | first=Jayanth | date=2009-07-26 | url=http://www.telegraphindia.com/1090726/jsp/frontpage/story_11283909.jsp | title=Delhi shuts out Uighur matriarch | work=The Telegraph (Kolkata) | accessdate=2010-01-29 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090826035912/http://www.telegraphindia.com/1090726/jsp/frontpage/story_11283909.jsp | archivedate=2009-08-26 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。北京也召见日本大使，抗议热比娅到访日本<ref>{{cite news | date=2009-07-28 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/8171791.stm | title=Uighur Kadeer arrives in Tokyo | publisher=BBC News | accessdate=2010-01-29 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120327111731/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/8171791.stm | archivedate=2012-03-27 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Teleg5943780/>。8月，热比娅到访澳大利亚宣传关于她的电影《爱的十个条件》，中国向澳大利亚政府提出交涉，要求对方将她的电影下架<ref name=Teleg5943780>{{cite news | url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/australiaandthepacific/australia/5943780/Australia-defies-China-to-host-Uighur-leader-Rebiya-Kadeer.html | title=Australia defies China to host Uighur leader Rebiya Kadeer | work=The Daily Telegraph | date=2009-07-31 | accessdate=2010-01-29 | location=London | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100523125041/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/australiaandthepacific/australia/5943780/Australia-defies-China-to-host-Uighur-leader-Rebiya-Kadeer.html | archivedate=2010-05-23 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

中国博客圈对骚乱的反应明显多于官方。尽管有网络封锁和审查，[[中华人民共和国网络审查|互联网监察者]]监视继续尝试发表对事件起因观点或表达对暴力行为愤怒的网民。尽管部分博客主立场亲政府，其他博客主更多地反映了事件的起因<ref name=onlineventire>{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2009/07/07/us-china-xinjiang-internet-idUSTRE5651K420090707 |title=Chinese go online to vent ire at Xinjiang unrest |agency=Reuters |date=2009-07-07 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110210034344/http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/07/07/us-china-xinjiang-internet-idUSTRE5651K420090707 |archivedate=2011-02-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。政府工作人员迅速在多个论坛和新闻网站上删掉骚乱的评论<ref name=onlineventire/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www1.voanews.com/english/news/a-13-2009-07-08-voa13-68819437.html?CFTOKEN=55253988&jsessionid=de302f61e608c19f44f12739d7fd6331a4cf&CFID=286996934 |publisher=VOA News |title=Chinese Authorities Blame Internet for Fanning Uighur Anger |date=2009-07-08 |accessdate=2010-01-18 }}{{Dead link|date=2019年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。这些呼吁的共同主题便是惩罚肇事者。部分帖子还提到备受汉族及其他民族尊重的将军[[王震|王震]]，有国际媒体报道称“许多维吾尔人害怕中国共产党会发动自[[新疆和平解放|1949年接管新疆]]后的新一轮压制”<ref name=onlineventire/>。

2010年3月2日，[[中国伊斯兰教协会|中国伊斯兰教协会]]会长[[陈广元|陈广元]]做客[[人民网|人民网]]强国论坛“走近政协”栏目，在针对网友询问其对乌鲁木齐“7·5”事件的看法时，陈广元表示：“这既不是民族问题、也不是宗教问题，这是因为一些分裂组织、极端主义分子造成的，他们只是打着民族和宗教的旗号而已。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.people.com.cn/GB/32306/143124/147550/11059488.html |title=人民网·陈广元谈人民政协民族和宗教工作 |accessdate=2020-05-18 |archive-date=2019-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613144342/http://www.people.com.cn/GB/32306/143124/147550/11059488.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 国际反应 ===
[[联合国秘书长|联合国秘书长]][[潘基文|潘基文]]敦促各方保持克制<ref name=jg>{{cite news |last=Martin |first=Dan |url=http://thejakartaglobe.com/afp/china-says-over-1400-arrested-for-xinjiang-riots/316662 |title=China says over 1,400 arrested for Xinjiang riots |work=Jakarta Globe |date=2009-07-06 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090710021534/http://thejakartaglobe.com/afp/china-says-over-1400-arrested-for-xinjiang-riots/316662 |archivedate=2009-07-10 }}</ref>，呼吁中国采取措施保护平民，尊重言论、集会和信息自由<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bt.com.bn/asia_news/2009/07/07/xinjiang_unrest_un_urges_china_to_respect_freedoms |title=Xinjiang unrest: UN urges China to respect freedoms |work=The Brunei Times |date=2009-07-07 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120113053330/http://www.bt.com.bn/asia_news/2009/07/07/xinjiang_unrest_un_urges_china_to_respect_freedoms |archivedate=2012-01-13 }}</ref>。[[联合国人权事务高级专员|人权事务高级专员]][[纳维·皮莱|纳维·皮莱]]表示对死亡人数高企的“担心”，指出“事发不到一天，遇害受伤人数非常高”<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2009/07/07/un-rights-chief-alarmed-death-toll-china.html | title=UN rights chief alarmed by death toll in China | work=Jakarta Post | agency=Associated Press | accessdate=2010-01-18 | date=2009-07-07 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090708002438/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2009/07/07/un-rights-chief-alarmed-death-toll-china.html | archivedate=2009-07-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=31381&Cr=Pillay&Cr1= |title=UN human rights chief alarmed by 'major tragedy' in western China |publisher=UN News Centre |date=2009-07-07 |access-date=2019-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223403/http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=31381&Cr=Pillay&Cr1= |archive-date=2016-03-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她也呼吁中国必须符合国际规范，人道对待拘留者<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.khaleejtimes.ae/DisplayArticleNew.asp?col=&section=international&xfile=data/international/2009/July/international_July567.xml |title=UN urges China, ethnic groups to halt violence |work=Khaleej Times |agency=Reuters |accessdate=2010-01-18 |date=2009-07-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725152650/http://www.khaleejtimes.ae/DisplayArticleNew.asp?col=&section=international&xfile=data%2Finternational%2F2009%2FJuly%2Finternational_July567.xml |archivedate=2011-07-25 }}</ref>。

[[上海合作组织|上海合作组织]]表达了对事件无辜遇害者家属的同情，表示组织各成员国认为新疆是中国不可分割的一部分，新疆局势纯粹是中国内部事务<ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-07/11/content_11693625.htm | title=SCO expresses condolence to families of victims in Xinjiang riot | agency=Xinhua | publisher=Chinaview.cn | accessdate=2010-01-18 | date=2009-07-11 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090717034941/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-07/11/content_11693625.htm | archivedate=2009-07-17 }}</ref>。[[俄罗斯外交部|俄罗斯外交部长]][[谢尔盖·维克托罗维奇·拉夫罗夫|谢尔盖·维克托罗维奇·拉夫罗夫]]谴责暴乱分子“使用分离主义标语，挑拨民族关系”<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2009/07/08/us-china-xinjiang-russia-sb-idUSTRE5671SM20090708 |title=Russia says China Xinjiang riots internal affair |agency=Reuters |date=2009-07-08 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |first=Guy |last=Faulconbridge |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110830044325/http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/07/08/us-china-xinjiang-russia-sb-idUSTRE5671SM20090708 |archive-date=2011-08-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。邻国[[哈萨克斯坦|哈萨克斯坦]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Kazakh Foreign Ministry: Above 1,000 Kazakh citizens leave Xinjiang due to riots |url=http://en.ca-news.org/news/76911 |website=Central Asia News |accessdate=2019-07-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120308144443/http://en.ca-news.org/news/76911 |archivedate=2012-03-08 |date=2009-07-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[吉尔吉斯斯坦|吉尔吉斯斯坦]]表示会防范“难民涌入”，加强边境管控<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/world/07/08/09/central-asia-uighurs-look-fury-bloodshed |title=Central Asia Uighurs look on with fury at bloodshed |publisher=ABS CBN News |agency=Agence France-Presse |accessdate=2010-01-18 |date=2009-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090711135126/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/world/07/08/09/central-asia-uighurs-look-fury-bloodshed |archive-date=2009-07-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rferl.org/content/Kyrgyz_Tighten_Controls_On_Chinese_Border/1772486.html |title=Kyrgyz Tighten Controls On Chinese Border |author=Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty |date=2009-07-08 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090806044602/http://www.rferl.org/content/Kyrgyz_Tighten_Controls_On_Chinese_Border/1772486.html |archive-date=2009-08-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。尽管哈萨克斯坦政府支持中国，5000多名维吾尔人于7月19日在当时的首都[[阿拉木图|阿拉木图]]抗议中国警察向示威者使用过分暴力<ref>{{cite news |url=http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/nationworld/2009499738_apaskazakhstanuighurprotest.html |title=Seattle Times | publisher=ABC News | agency=Associated Press | last=Leonard | first=Peter |date=2009-07-19 |accessdate=2009-07-19}}</ref>。

[[伊斯兰会议组织|伊斯兰会议组织]]谴责“不成比例地使用武力”，呼吁北京“迅速将肇事者绳之以法”，敦促中国调查事件起因，找到解决骚乱的办法<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/afp_asiapacific/view/441067/1/.html |title=World powers call for restraint amid China unrest |publisher=Channel News Asia |date=2009-07-08 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090913121426/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/afp_asiapacific/view/441067/1/.html |archive-date=2009-09-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[欧盟|欧盟]]领导人表示担忧，敦促中国政府在处理示威者时表现克制<ref name=ra>{{cite news | url=http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/connectasia/stories/200907/s2618918.htm | title=International reaction to Uyghur protest violence | publisher=Radio Australia | format=音频 | accessdate=2010-01-18 | date=2009-07-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090719120633/http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/connectasia/stories/200907/s2618918.htm | archive-date=2009-07-19 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.sinodaily.com/2006/090707135555.gaex23r3.html |title=France concerned over Xinjiang riots |work=Sino Daily |date=2009-07-07 |accessdate=2014-12-19 |agency=Agence France-Presse |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220120808/http://www.sinodaily.com/2006/090707135555.gaex23r3.html |archive-date=2014-12-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。德国总理[[安格拉·默克尔|安格拉·默克尔]]呼吁尊重少数民族人权<ref name=et/>。意大利总统[[乔治·纳波利塔诺|乔治·纳波利塔诺]]和胡锦涛出席记者会时提到人权问题，表示“中国取得的经济和社会发展给人权带来新的要求”<ref name=rfe>{{cite news | url=http://www.rferl.org/content/Kyrgyz_Uyghur_Sees_Roots_Of_China_Unrest_In_Beijing_Policies/1770623.html | title=Uyghurs Abroad Blame China Policies For Unrest | author=Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty | date=2009-07-07 | accessdate=2010-01-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090810203943/http://www.rferl.org/content/Kyrgyz_Uyghur_Sees_Roots_Of_China_Unrest_In_Beijing_Policies/1770623.html | archive-date=2009-08-10 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.norwaypost.no/news/norway-concerned-about-violence-in-xinjiang.html |title=Norway concerned about violence in Xinjiang |work=Norway Post |publisher=Norwegian Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-07-09 |accessdate=2009-09-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118071128/http://www.norwaypost.no/news/norway-concerned-about-violence-in-xinjiang.html |archivedate=2012-01-18 }}</ref>。

[[土耳其|土耳其]]表示“很悲伤”，要求中国当局将肇事者绳之以法<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.todayszaman.com/newsDetail_getNewsById.action?load=detay&link=180125&bolum=100 |title=Tension runs high as China cracks down on Uighur riot |publisher=Today's Zaman |date=2009-07-07 |accessdate=2011-04-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120308124949/http://www.todayszaman.com/newsDetail_getNewsById.action?load=detay&link=180125&bolum=100 |archivedate=2012-03-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.etaiwannews.com/etn/news_content.php?id=997938&lang=eng_news |title=Turkish FM calls on China to end violence |work=Taiwan News |agency=Associated Press |accessdate=2010-01-18 |date=2009-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090710175755/http://www.etaiwannews.com/etn/news_content.php?id=997938&lang=eng_news |archive-date=2009-07-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。总理[[雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安|雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安]]表示事件“犹如种族灭绝”<ref>{{cite news |title=Turkish PM compares violence in China to genocide |url=http://www.wsvn.com/news/articles/world/MI125641/ |agency=Associated Press |date=2009-07-10 |accessdate=2009-09-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090713190636/http://www.wsvn.com/news/articles/world/MI125641/ |archivedate=2009-07-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=2009-07-10 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |title=Turkey attacks China 'genocide' |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/8145451.stm |publisher=BBC News |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090930100049/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/8145451.stm |archive-date=2009-09-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，贸易和工业部长{{le|尼哈特·埃尔贡|Nihat Ergün}}呼吁抵制中国货物<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.todayszaman.com/newsDetail_getNewsById.action?load=detay&link=180534 |title=Turkey calls for boycott of Chinese goods |date=2009-07-09 |work=Today's Zaman |accessdate=2010-01-18 |agency=Associated Press |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120308123508/http://www.todayszaman.com/newsDetail_getNewsById.action?load=detay&link=180534 |archivedate=2012-03-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.france24.com/en/20090710-turkish-pm-erdogan-xinjiang-violence-genocide-turkey-uighurs-han-trade-beijing-china |title=Turkish PM Erdogan likens Xinjiang violence to 'genocide' |date=2009-07-10 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |agency=Agence France-Presse |work=France 24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090715024442/http://www.france24.com/en/20090710-turkish-pm-erdogan-xinjiang-violence-genocide-turkey-uighurs-han-trade-beijing-china |archive-date=2009-07-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。相当多的[[土耳其人|土耳其人]]聚集抗议反对中国，活动大多针对土耳其各大城市的中国使领馆。土耳其的立场引发中国媒体强烈抗议<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/b2fe933a-70d5-11de-9717-00144feabdc0.html |work=Financial Times |title=China fury at Turkey's 'genocide' comments |first=Kathrin |last=Hille |first2=Delphine |last2=Strauss |date=2009-07-15 |accessdate=2009-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090718105433/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/b2fe933a-70d5-11de-9717-00144feabdc0.html |archive-date=2009-07-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |work=The Malaysian Insider |title=Turkey PM told to retract Xinjiang 'genocide' claim |date=2009-07-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2009/07/14/us-china-xinjiang-idUSTRE56D0QJ20090714?feedType=RSS&feedName=worldNews |title=China dismisses accusation of Xinjiang genocide |publisher=Reuters |date=2009-07-14 |accessdate=2009-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111072947/http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/07/14/us-china-xinjiang-idUSTRE56D0QJ20090714?feedType=RSS&feedName=worldNews |archive-date=2014-11-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。热比娅认为，土耳其干涉维吾尔事务受到阻碍，这是对中国干涉[[土耳其-库尔德冲突|库尔德问题]]的报复<ref>{{cite book |last=Kadeer |first=Rebiya |title=Dragon Fighter One Woman's Epic Struggle for Peace with China |url=https://archive.org/details/dragonfighterone0000kade |year=2009 |publisher=Kales Press |isbn=978-0-9798456-1-1 |page=[https://archive.org/details/dragonfighterone0000kade/page/273 273]}}</ref>。不过尼尔根发动的抵制中国货物的行动失败了<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2014/10/turkey-kuwait-ambassador-traffic-brawl-army-pilot.html |title=Will Kuwaiti diplomat's road rage hurt Turkish economy? |accessdate=2015-10-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150922233732/http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2014/10/turkey-kuwait-ambassador-traffic-brawl-army-pilot.html |archivedate=2015-09-22 }}</ref>。

伊斯兰会议组织的阿拉伯国家在政治上支持中国，沙特阿拉伯和埃及还特别压制了[[伊斯兰合作组织|伊斯兰合作组织]]针对维吾尔人提出的任何反华动议。埃及也认为自己有着像中国一样的内部宗派问题，苏丹也担心外部势力插手内部事务，印尼被迫和国内的伊斯兰主义者打交道，强调不存在宗教冲突，没有新疆的民族骚乱，借此来平息事态<ref name="wikileaks">{{cite web|url=https://wikileaks.org/plusd/cables/09BEIJING2041_a.html|title=Cable: 09BEIJING2041_a|publisher=wikileaks.org|accessdate=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160111221529/https://wikileaks.org/plusd/cables/09BEIJING2041_a.html|archive-date=2016-01-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巴基斯坦、沙特阿拉伯和埃及帮助中国取消伊斯兰会议组织上一份针对新疆局势的声明<ref name="wikileaks2">{{cite web|url=https://www.wikileaks.org/plusd/cables/09BEIJING2185_a.html|title=Cable: 09BEIJING2185_a|publisher=wikileaks.org|accessdate=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160111221531/https://www.wikileaks.org/plusd/cables/09BEIJING2185_a.html|archive-date=2016-01-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[阿拉伯联盟|阿拉伯联盟]]、沙特阿拉伯和伊朗没有针对局势作公开回应，鉴于伊朗和沙特阿拉伯在伊斯兰世界的影响力，中国和两国建立了更深厚的关系<ref name="Al-Tamimi2013">{{cite book|author=Naser M. Al-Tamimi|title=China-Saudi Arabia Relations, 1990-2012: Marriage of Convenience Or Strategic Alliance?|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=tYuwAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA92&dq=uyghur+pressure+marriage&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CDcQ6AEwA2oVChMIqbfH4ZPLyAIVDHM-Ch2zgwgG#v=onepage&q=uyghur%20pressure%20marriage&f=false|date=2013-09-05|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-134-46153-0|pages=92–|access-date=2019-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109200444/https://books.google.com/books?id=tYuwAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA92&dq=uyghur+pressure+marriage&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CDcQ6AEwA2oVChMIqbfH4ZPLyAIVDHM-Ch2zgwgG#v=onepage&q=uyghur%20pressure%20marriage&f=false|archive-date=2017-01-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

阿富汗<ref name=afghan>{{cite news |url=http://en.trend.az/news/world/afghanistan/1501282.html |title=Afghanistan supports China's territorial integrity |work=Trend News |date=2009-07-08 |accessdate=2010-01-18 }}{{Dead link|date=2020年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>、柬埔寨<ref name=cambod>{{cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-07/11/content_11693729.htm |title=China taking appropriate measures in Xinjiang: Cambodian gov't |agency=Xinhua |publisher=Chinaview.cn |accessdate=2010-01-18 |date=2009-07-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090715064958/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-07/11/content_11693729.htm |archivedate=2009-07-15 }}</ref>和越南相信中国政府会“采取合适措施”<ref name=viet>{{cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-07/08/content_11673383.htm |title=Vietnam expresses support for China's handling of Xinjiang unrest |agency=Xinhua |publisher=Chinaview.cn |accessdate=2010-01-18 |date=2009-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090712015326/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-07/08/content_11673383.htm |archive-date=2009-07-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，支持“中国领土主权和完整”<ref name=afghan/>。密克罗尼西亚联邦副主席{{le|阿利克·阿利克|Alik Alik}}谴责事件是“恐怖主义行为”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-07/09/content_11681728.htm |title=Micronesia vice president condemns Xinjiang riot |date=2009-07-09 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |publisher=Chinaview.cn |agency=Xinhua |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090829152109/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-07/09/content_11681728.htm |archivedate=2009-08-29 }}</ref>。

